{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"c3a2794f72","title":"王力传达毛主席对广播系统的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"4391749f66","index":0,"year":1967,"month":1,"day":30,"articleId":"c3a2794f72"}],"tags":[{"id":"20ebde32a6","name":"王力","type":"人物"},{"id":"268718f23b","name":"新闻广播和出版","type":"主题"},{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库(第一版)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"},{"id":"fa147b61e7","name":"王力"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"beb5abe82e","type":"title","text":"王力传达毛主席对广播系统的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c3a2794f72"},{"id":"7e47269e31","type":"paragraph","text":"中央电台的革命同志夺了权，很好！听说现在又要分裂，内部吵，还有广播学院。革命派掌了权，又分裂，要劝他们团结，以大局为重，要搞大团体主义，不要搞小团体主义。管他反对不反对自己，反对自己反对错了的人，也要善于和他们团结，反对自己的人，就不能合作，我就不赞成。","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c3a2794f72"}],"page":{"id":"483edf60d6","publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c3a2794f72","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}